<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org0fc7625">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Can get new list item with <code>M-RET</code></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgf38152d" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgf38152d">Agenda</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgf38152d">
<p>
When in the agenda view, you can use:
</p>

<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-left" />

<col  class="org-left" />
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">key</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">action</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">f</td>
<td class="org-left">Move forward one day</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">b</td>
<td class="org-left">Move backward one day</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">.</td>
<td class="org-left">Jump to today</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">'/'</td>
<td class="org-left">Filter task by tag</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<p>
Can filter tasks by tag in agenda mode using <code>/</code>
OR can use org-agenda <code>m</code> to filter by tags
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org1951d6f" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org1951d6f">Basic Bookmark Operations</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org1951d6f">
<p>
Creating bookmarks:
</p>

<p>
<code>C-x r m</code> (bookmark-set) - Set a bookmark at the current location
You'll be prompted to name the bookmark
</p>

<p>
Can goto bookmarks form <code>consult-buffer</code>
</p>

<p>
Managing bookmarks:
</p>

<p>
M-x bookmark-delete - Delete a bookmark
M-x bookmark-rename - Rename a bookmark
</p>
</div>
</div>

